creator: 365 Retail Markets
descriptionHtml:
Market Connect is a new app to make purchasing food and ordering ahead more convenient than ever before. If you see the Market Connect logo at any of our service locations, you can use the app to:
- Create and fund your account
- Scan and Pay for items within your market
- View your purchase history
- Order Ahead at your café location
Look for the logo and get started today!
descriptionShort: Market Connect makes purchasing food & ordering ahead more convenient than ever.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• You can now associate a market card or scan code to your GMA account via the app.
• Users are now required to verify their email addresses as a part of GMA to help verify identity.
• We updated the Location Code value, used to link Home Locations & Order Ahead, to help provide clarity & unique values.
• Added helpful icons to the cart & checkout screens to show dine-in, to-go, or both.

Market Connect is a new app to make purchasing food and ordering ahead more convenient than ever before. If you see the Market Connect logo at any of our service locations, you can use the app to:
- Create and fund your account
- Scan and Pay for items within your market
- View your purchase history
- Order Ahead at your café location
Look for the logo and get started today!
descriptionShort: Market Connect makes purchasing food & ordering ahead more convenient than ever.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Added security for account creation. Upon email verification you will be redirected and required to login before completing the account creation process.
Items within the cart screen now have an X in addition to the swiping function for deleting a specific item.
Fixed PicoVend Mini product information display issues within the app.
